snippet.title: Open Alpha Week One Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Team Vortex. With your input and feedback during our Open Alpha Week One we will iterate on Rushdown Revolt to make it the most electric, expressive and combo-centric fighting game we can collectively dream up. 

Download and play it for free on Steam PC: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1376070/Rushdown_Revolt__Alpha_Testing/
